    Class Description
    QLApi
    The class QLApi contains methods for getting information about the QuickLink API.

    The Class QLBoolean contains a boolean type with support functions for use with QuickLink.

    A QLCalibration object is a container for holding calibration data used by QLDevice objects.
    QLCalibrationScore
    The class QLCalibrationScore contains values that identify the quality of a calibration at a target.
    QLCalibrationTarget
    The class QLCalibrationTarget contains data that identifies a target and its location.

    The Class QLCalibrationTargetStatus contains status information for a calibration target.

    The Class QLCalibrationType defines the available calibration types.

    The Class QLColor defines a Color object for use in QuickLink.
